# Prosper Patterns

## Environment

All commands run inside Docker — **no PHP/Node on host**.

```bash
docker exec prosper_app_dev <cmd>
make npm cmd="..."
```

## CRUD Controller Pattern (DTO Hierarchy)

New resources use `BaseWebCrudDto` (Spatie Data). Child controllers MUST redeclare typed properties.

```php
<?php

declare(strict_types=1);

namespace App\Http\Controllers\Web\Module;

use App\DTOs\Requests\CreateExampleDto;
use App\DTOs\Resources\ExampleDto;
use App\Models\Module\Example;
use App\Services\BaseWebCrudDto;

class ExampleController extends BaseWebCrudDto
{
    public string $model = Example::class;
    public string $viewPath = 'Module/Example';
    public string $viewEdit = '/Create';
    public string $resourceDto = ExampleDto::class;
    public string $storeDto = CreateExampleDto::class;
    public string $updateDto = CreateExampleDto::class;
    public string $modelKey = 'uuid';
    public bool $use_redirect = false;
    /** @var array<string> */
    public array $searchAble = ['name', 'code'];
    public bool $autoCache = true;
}
```

## Model Pattern

```php
<?php

declare(strict_types=1);

namespace App\Models\Module;

use App\Traits\HasBaseOwner;
use App\Traits\HasBaseTable;
use Illuminate\Database\Eloquent\Model;
use Spatie\Activitylog\Traits\LogsActivity;

class Example extends Model
{
    use HasBaseOwner, HasBaseTable, LogsActivity;

    protected $fillable = [
        'name', 'code',
        // HasBaseOwner fields (always include all 6):
        'created_at', 'updated_at', 'deleted_at',
        'created_by', 'updated_by', 'deleted_by',
    ];
}
```

## DTO Pattern

### Resource DTO
```php
<?php

declare(strict_types=1);

namespace App\DTOs\Resources;

use App\Traits\HasDtoPrepareTrait;
use Spatie\LaravelData\Contracts\DataPreparableInterface;
use Spatie\LaravelData\Data;

class ExampleDto extends Data implements DataPreparableInterface
{
    use HasDtoPrepareTrait;

    public function __construct(
        public ?int $id,
        public ?string $uuid,
        public ?string $name,
        public ?string $code,
    ) {}
}
```

### Request DTO
```php
<?php

declare(strict_types=1);

namespace App\DTOs\Requests;

use Spatie\LaravelData\Data;

class CreateExampleDto extends Data
{
    public function __construct(
        public string $name,
        public ?string $code,
    ) {}

    public static function rules(): array
    {
        return [
            'name' => ['required', 'string', 'max:255'],
        ];
    }
}
```

## Frontend API Pattern

```ts
// resources/js/apis/example.api.ts
import route from 'ziggy-js'

export const exampleApi = {
    index: (params?: object) => route('module.examples.index', params),
    store: () => route('module.examples.store'),
    update: (params: { uuid: string }) => route('module.examples.update', params),
    destroy: (params: { uuid: string }) => route('module.examples.destroy', params),
}
```

## Frontend Page Pattern

```vue
<!-- resources/js/Pages/Module/Example/Index.vue -->
<script setup lang="ts">
import { ref } from 'vue'
import { usePage } from '@inertiajs/vue3'
import TabulatorSimple from '@/Components/TabulatorSimple/TabulatorSimple.vue'
import IndexBaseLayout from '@/Components/IndexBaseLayout.vue'
import { exampleApi } from '@/apis/example.api'

const page = usePage()
</script>
```

## TypeScript Interface Pattern

```ts
// resources/js/types/module.ts
export interface Example {
    id: number
    uuid: string
    name: string
    code: string | null
    created_at: string
    updated_at: string
}
```

## i18n Pattern

Translations in `resources/js/i18n/{domain}/{locale}.ts` — locales are `en` and `id`.

```ts
// resources/js/i18n/module/en.ts
export default {
    example: {
        title: 'Examples',
        name: 'Name',
        code: 'Code',
    },
}
```

## Routes Pattern

```php
// routes/Web/Module/route.php
Route::resource('examples', ExampleController::class);

// routes/Api/Module/route.php
Route::apiResource('examples', ExampleController::class);
```

## Known Gotchas

| Gotcha | Fix |
|--------|-----|
| PHP & Node.js not on host | Use `docker exec prosper_app_dev <cmd>` |
| AutoCompleteInput refs not populated | Call `setQuery()` after `nextTick` |
| PHPStan cascades from base class | Fix `BaseCrud`/`BaseCrudDto` errors first |
| Child controllers missing typed properties | MUST redeclare typed properties matching base class |
| Decimal part stripped as Number | Never convert decimal part to `Number` in CurrencyInput2 |
| Litepicker range not displayed | Check for ` - ` separator before parsing as single date |
| `team` stored as name string | `closing.team` and `dncn.team` are team `name`, not `team.id` |
| `approval_status` is int-backed enum | Cast to enum in model `$casts` |
| `pointer-events-none` hides file links | Use `:disabled` on individual inputs instead |
| `unset_array` strips fields | Check `__prepareDataStore`'s `unset_array` if a field isn't saving |
| TomSelect hidden in overflow-hidden | Change filter card to `overflow-visible`, add `!z-[60]` |
| API_SERVICE is raw axios | No interceptor unwrap — access `response.data` manually |

## Auth & Team Gating

```php
// Policy check
$user->hasRole('manager') && $user->teams->contains('name', $closing->team);
```

```ts
// Frontend check
const canApprove = computed(() =>
    auth.role === 'manager' && auth.teams.some(t => t.name === data.team)
)
```

Roles: `manager` (team-scoped), `finance` (finance team), `ceo` (global), staff (default).

## CRUD Checklist (New Resource)

1. Migration — `database/migrations/{Module}/`
2. Model — `app/Models/{Module}/` with `HasBaseOwner`, `HasBaseTable`, `LogsActivity`
3. Resource DTO — `app/DTOs/Resources/{Name}Dto.php`
4. Request DTO — `app/DTOs/Requests/Create{Name}Dto.php`
5. Web Controller — `app/Http/Controllers/Web/{Module}/` extends `BaseWebCrudDto`
6. API Controller — `app/Http/Controllers/Api/{Module}/` extends `BaseCrudDto`
7. Policy — `app/Policies/{Module}/` → register in `AuthServiceProvider`
8. Routes — `routes/{Web,Api}/{Module}/route.php`
9. Frontend API — `resources/js/apis/{name}.api.ts`
10. Frontend Page — `resources/js/Pages/{Module}/{Name}/Index.vue` + `Create.vue`
11. TypeScript types — `resources/js/types/{module}.ts`
12. i18n — `resources/js/i18n/{module}/{en,id}.ts`

